<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-8">What is Clever Cycle?</h1>
    <p>The Clever Cycle is an application that allows you to plan parenthood by specifying fertile days. It uses a natural double-check method that is based on calculations and the following symptoms: temperature, bleeding, mucus, hardness and the position of the cervix.</p>
